교재 및 참고문헌: Course materials will be uploaded to YSCEC and/or sent to your via KakaoTalk chat room for our class.  Make sure you have access to Adobe Acrobat Reader, Video playing app, Microsoft Word and PowerPoint. You should bring something to write with and something to write on to take notes during class discussions and lectures. In-class materials will not be provided for you on YSCEC or KakaoTalk.  Occasionally, in class, you will need a notebook computer with Internet access or a smart phone with Kakao Talk to complete the speech scripts, outlines, and audience analysis. KakaoTalk is the most effective way to communicate with me and your classmates both in and out of class.
